codex
I’ve reached the important constraint boundary: the theft path is straightforward, but fungible profit is not guaranteed by the bug itself. I’m writing the verifier so it dynamically proves the unauthorized purchase on the fork when the preconditions exist, uses only verifier-held assets for funding, and leaves `profitAmount()` at zero unless an actual net-positive token gain is realized.
